## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **xanomeline + trospium KarXT Cobenfy 2024** = first FDA muscarinic M1/M4 — first non-D2 antipsychotic paradigm shift in 70+ years (chlorpromazine 1954 D2 dogma 종결). Karuna Therapeutics → BMS acquisition. quantum-VQE 의 muscarinic GPCR pocket leverage.
2. **emraclidine 2024 EMPOWER Phase 3 primary fail** = AbbVie/Cerevel M4 selective — KarXT positive 후 second M4 selective 가 동일 disease 에서 fail. M4 selective dose-finding + patient stratification 미흡 가설. quantum-VQE 의 M4 selectivity revisit needed.
3. **ulotaront SEP-363856 2023 Phase 3 fail** = Sumitomo/Otsuka TAAR1 + 5HT1A — Breakthrough Designation 후 confirmatory fail. trace amine receptor paradigm 의 임상 challenge. quantum-VQE 의 TAAR1 pocket revisit.
4. **clozapine 1989 TRS standard** = first atypical + first FDA TRS — 35+ year gold standard but agranulocytosis monitoring (REMS) + myocarditis (cross-myocarditis_specific) + metabolic burden. quantum-VQE 의 D2/5HT2A pocket 분리 challenge.
5. **lumateperone Caplyta 2019 + 2021 bipolar** = ITI-007 → ITI-Lumateperone first-in-class 5HT2A + D1/D2 partial — schizophrenia 2019 + bipolar depression 2021 확장. metabolic burden 적은 atypical alternative.
6. **paliperidone palmitate 1m+3m+6m + aripiprazole lauroxil + olanzapine pamoate LAI 2009-2021** = schizophrenia LAI paradigm 확장 — adherence + relapse prevention + court-ordered (cross-forensic_psychiatry). 6-monthly Hafyera 2021 = longest LAI.
7. **D3-preferring cariprazine 2015 + brexpiprazole 2015** = D2 partial agonist 2nd-gen — aripiprazole 2002 후 13-year gap. quantum-VQE 의 D2 vs D3 selectivity.
8. **valbenazine + deutetrabenazine 2017 first FDA TD** = VMAT2 first FDA tardive dyskinesia — antipsychotic 70-year era 의 EPS sequelae 늦은 약물. cross-iag VMAT2.
9. **pimavanserin Nuplazid 2016 first FDA PD psychosis** = 5HT2A inverse agonist + D2-free — PD psychosis (cross-dementia_specific) first non-D2 antipsychotic. schizophrenia adjunct fail history (ENHANCE Phase 3 fail 2019).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, schizophrenia spectrum 임상 의미 한정. KarXT + emraclidine + ulotaront 비교 in-silico 가능성만.

